Intelligence sources tipped the Nation that Mr Kang’ata had since December 15 become panicky after Tangatanga shrugged off opposition by Kieleweke, the Handshake and Governor Mwangi wa Iria’s Civic Renewal Party (CRP) to win the Gaturi by-election. 



